          • [ - ] Senior - member since 31-Dec-15

            @Pastore10 Messi's finish skill better than Neymar but in this game the two solo situation are very different: First Neymar started from left side line, near Barca's penalty erea. Messi started near center circle. The distance that Neymar has to cover is much more than Messi. 2. When Neymar has ball inside Celta Vigo's final thirst, there were 5 defenders focus on him. No other Barca player available support him. However, when Messi ran to Celta Vigo penalty area. There were 5 defenders too. But two of them take a look at the other Barca players in case of Messi pass the ball to his teammate. And the result is Messi had space to shot. Note: Football is not an individual game. Evaluate a situation or a player, must be observe his teammate's action and opponents' action too
